Titolo: Shadow Sorcerer

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Shadow Sorcerer is a role-playing video game published in 1991 by Strategic Simulations. The game is the sequel to Heroes of the Lance and Dragons of Flame. It is based on the third and fourth  Dragonlance campaign modules, Dragons of Hope and Dragons of Desolation.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
